---
---
<section id="who-its-for" class="px-6 py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-border">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
		<p class="eyebrow text-center">Who it's for</p>
		<h2 class="heading-lg text-center mt-3">Built for how you work</h2>
		<p class="body-lg text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">Whether you ship code, manage clients, or run a company — AEOrank fits your workflow.</p>

		<div class="space-y-6 mt-14">

			<!-- Developer Panel -->
			<div class="card p-8 md:p-10 border-l-4 border-l-accent grid md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] gap-10 animate-on-scroll">
				<div>
					<p class="eyebrow text-xs">FOR DEVELOPERS</p>
					<h3 class="heading-md mt-2">AEO in your pipeline. Not your browser.</h3>
					<p class="text-text-muted mt-2 text-sm">The only AEO tool that lives in your terminal, your CI, and your framework — not a SaaS dashboard you forget to check.</p>
					<ul class="mt-6 space-y-5">
						<li class="flex gap-4">
							<span class="text-accent text-lg shrink-0 mt-0.5">&lt;/&gt;</span>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-sm">CLI-first, zero magic</p>
								<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1"><code class="!text-[10px]">npx aeorank-cli scan &lt;url&gt;</code> — runs anywhere, no account, no API key. Colored output with per-criterion scores.</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-4">
							<span class="text-accent text-lg shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x2387;</span>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Block AEO regressions in CI</p>
								<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">GitHub App: one-click, zero YAML. GitHub Action: <code class="!text-[10px]">fail-below</code> thresholds. Both post Check Runs with full breakdowns.</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-4">
							<span class="text-accent text-lg shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x25C8;</span>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-sm">13 framework plugins, 3 lines of config</p>
								<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Next.js, Astro, Nuxt, and 10 more. Serves all 9 generated files at your site root on build. MIT licensed, self-hostable.</p>
							</div>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-6">
					<div class="card p-5 !bg-white/[0.04] !border-0">
						<p class="text-sm text-text-secondary italic">"Dropped it in next.config.ts, ran the CI check, and caught a robots.txt regression before it shipped."</p>
						<footer class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-3">— Senior engineer, DevTools startup</footer>
						<span class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mt-3 block">411 tests. Same score every run.</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
						<a href="https://github.com/apps/aeorank" class="btn-primary justify-center text-sm">Install GitHub App</a>
						<a href="https://docs.aeorank.dev/getting-started" class="btn-secondary justify-center text-sm">Read the Docs</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Agency Panel -->
			<div class="card p-8 md:p-10 border-l-4 border-l-[#6366F1] grid md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] gap-10 animate-on-scroll">
				<div>
					<p class="eyebrow text-xs" style="color: #6366F1">FOR AGENCIES</p>
					<h3 class="heading-md mt-2">Client AI visibility reports. In 30 seconds per site.</h3>
					<p class="text-text-muted mt-2 text-sm">Scan any client URL, get a scored report across 36 criteria, and deliver AI optimization as a service — using a free tool you can self-host.</p>
					<ul class="mt-6 space-y-5">
						<li class="flex gap-4">
							<span class="text-[#6366F1] text-lg shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x1F4CA;</span>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Benchmark clients against competitors</p>
								<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Our Scoreboard shows 100 funded startups averaging 42/100. Your clients are probably invisible to AI. Now you have the data to prove it.</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-4">
							<span class="text-[#6366F1] text-lg shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x1F4C4;</span>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Deliverable files, not dashboard links</p>
								<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Every scan generates 9 production files — llms.txt, schema.json, ai.txt, robots patch. Hand them to the client. They deploy. You look like a wizard.</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-4">
							<span class="text-[#6366F1] text-lg shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x221E;</span>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Unlimited scans. $0 tool cost.</p>
								<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">No per-seat pricing. No API credits. The CLI is MIT licensed. Scan 500 clients per month for free. Keep the margin.</p>
							</div>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-6">
					<div class="card p-5 !bg-white/[0.04] !border-0">
						<p class="text-sm text-text-secondary italic">"We added AEO audits to our SEO retainer. Clients love the score — they understand 67/100 immediately."</p>
						<footer class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-3">— Founder, boutique digital agency</footer>
						<span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#6366F1] mt-3 block">Avg industry score: 42/100</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
						<a href="https://docs.aeorank.dev/getting-started" class="btn-primary justify-center text-sm" style="background: #6366F1">Scan a Client Site Free</a>
						<a href="/scoreboard" class="btn-secondary justify-center text-sm">See Industry Benchmarks</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Founder Panel -->
			<div class="card p-8 md:p-10 border-l-4 border-l-[#FFD700] grid md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] gap-10 animate-on-scroll">
				<div>
					<p class="eyebrow text-xs" style="color: #FFD700">FOR FOUNDERS</p>
					<h3 class="heading-md mt-2">ChatGPT recommends your competitors. Not you.</h3>
					<p class="text-text-muted mt-2 text-sm">AI search drives 40% of web discovery and converts at 15.9% — higher than Google. Your score tells you how visible you are. The generated files start fixing it immediately.</p>
					<ul class="mt-6 space-y-5">
						<li class="flex gap-4">
							<span class="text-[#FFD700] text-lg shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x1F3AF;</span>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-sm">A number you can actually act on</p>
								<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Your AEO score is 0–100, graded A+ through F. You see exactly which criteria you're failing and why. No vague advice — specific gaps, ranked by impact.</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-4">
							<span class="text-[#FFD700] text-lg shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x1F4C8;</span>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Your competitors are scoring 42/100 on average</p>
								<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">We scanned 100 funded startups. Stripe scores 57. OpenAI scores 16. If billion-dollar companies are invisible to AI, your site probably is too — and it's fixable in an afternoon.</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-4">
							<span class="text-[#FFD700] text-lg shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x26A1;</span>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-sm">30 seconds to your first score</p>
								<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">No account, no credit card, no sales call. Gartner predicts 50% decline in organic search traffic by 2028. This is the fix.</p>
							</div>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-6">
					<div class="card p-5 !bg-white/[0.04] !border-0">
						<p class="text-sm text-text-secondary italic">"Had no idea AI couldn't see my site. Scored 31/100, fixed the llms.txt and schema, rescanned at 68 in one afternoon. Now we show up in Perplexity answers."</p>
						<footer class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-3">— Founder, B2B SaaS (pre-Series A)</footer>
						<span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#FFD700] mt-3 block">31 → 68 in one afternoon</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
						<a href="https://github.com/apps/aeorank" class="btn-primary justify-center text-sm" style="background: #CA8A04">Check My Score — Free</a>
						<a href="/scoreboard" class="btn-secondary justify-center text-sm">See How Others Score</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</section>
